<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/logo_smpdw.png">
  <title>Ketuntasan Tugas</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .alert {
      background-color: #ecfdf5;
      border-left: 5px solid #10b981;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #065f46;
    }

    .card {
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .card.green {
      background-color: #047857;
    }

    .card.dark {
      background-color: #0f172a;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: white;
      color: black;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .btn span {
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="alert">
    <strong>Informasi!</strong> Halaman perbaikan siswa
  </div>

  <div class="card green">
    <h2>Perbaikan Semester</h2>
    <p>Silahkan cek tugas perbaikan semester disini</p>
    <a href="https://forms.gle/eUNZfdCqz3j4xjcx8" class="btn">Lihat Detail <span>→</span></a>
  </div>

  <div class="card dark">
    <h2>Kekurangan Tugas Harian</h2>
    <p>Silahkan cek nama siswa yang masih memiliki kekurangan tugas harian disini</p>
    <a href="/tugas" class="btn">Lihat Detail <span>→</span></a>
  </div>

</body>

</html>